            <title>[LOG4J2-311] FastFileAppender and FastRollingFileAppender not thread-safe</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-311</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;FastFileManager#flush method needs to be synchronized.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m seeing the exception below. This can only happen if two threads modify the ByteBuffer simultaneously.&lt;/p&gt;

